name: Rene Makela Collection
description: René Alvarez Mäkelä is a spanish artist. His work has an influence on pop culture and street art. He has painted for singer Madonna, model Cara Delevigne, sports stars Cam Newton (NFL), Austin Rivers (NBA), Matt Kemp and Manny Machado (MLB), and brands such as Ron Barceló and Porsche. Now Pope Francis also has one of his works.
